Loop
through the elements of the array @samp{EXPR}, binding @samp{VAR} as a @code{setf}-able
place.

@samp{KEYS} is one or several of @samp{from}, @samp{upfrom}, @samp{downfrom}, @samp{to}, @samp{upto},
